window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Nine-year-old Louis Drax lies in a coma in a hospital bed, re-living the events that led to his near-fatal fall into a ravine. Despite being attracted to the boy's mother Natalie Drax, Louis' doctor, Pascal Dannachet, begins reluctantly to question her version of Louis' accident and the apparent culpability of her missing husband. </p> <p>As the boy struggles to communicate from within his coma, the chilling truth emerges....</p>"; 
